的项目报告还没写完，或者为了准备考试而熬夜复习。 2. 心理上的压力也会导致晚睡，总是担心工作或学习的事情，大脑处于紧张状态，难以放松进入睡眠。 三、不良的生活习惯 1. 晚上喝咖啡、茶等含有咖啡因的饮料，会让人精神振奋，难以入睡。 2. 没有固定的睡眠时间，作息不规律，导致生物钟紊乱。比如有时候早睡，有时候又很晚才睡，身体无法适应规律的睡眠节奏。 四、环境因素 1. 周围环境嘈杂、光线过亮或温度不适宜，会影响睡眠质量，让人难以入睡。例如，住在靠近马路的地方，晚上车辆噪音较大；或者房间的灯光太亮，没有营造出适合睡眠的氛围。 2. 睡前进行剧烈运动，会使身体处于兴奋状态，也不利于入睡。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6d128afe30f235015e54539ac45a116f_xl.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "27 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/732245137"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIsKrMkaauxalJEAMaCTExMDkyNTMxMyCy+/q3BjAAOIoBQAxyCTczMjI0NTEzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1728047914.617299", "card_id": "Q_559579842", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《封神演义》女娲让妲己祸害商朝，成功后为什么又杀了妲己？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-76e8b5267d9ad3d5bca2d79345b20697_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/559579842"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IsKrMkaauxalJEAMaCDg2NjMzNzMwIOW4qJoGMAA4bEANcgk1NTk1Nzk4NDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1728047914.617467", "card_id": "Q_668137539", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 96}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何给不懂棒球的人说明大谷翔平的厉害?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "只看过几部运动漫，不了解棒球规则的人"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d779a0b6cf2ac886c51faf0c194a8e55_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.z